      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>剝，不利有攸往。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Bo indicates that (in the state which it symbolises) it will not be advantageous to make a movement in any direction whatever.</seg>
