      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：剝牀以足，蔑貞凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows one overturning the couch by injuring its legs. (The injury will go on to) the destruction of (all) firm correctness, and there will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
